description: A teenage boy contracted by Easter to find the Embryo. He often helps Amu even though he works for Easter. Ikuto actually despises Easter and tries to wrench himself free from them by trying to find the Embryo to grant his own wish. He possesses the Dumpty Key which pairs with Amu`s Humpty Lock which at first did not fit in the keyhole. Like his father, Ikuto is a skilled violinist.
name: Tsukiyomi Ikuto
